#. Translators: Deactivation is a permanent action that occurs on the server.
#: src/account_settings/general_page/deactivate_account_subpage.blp:45
msgid ""
"Deactivating your account means you will lose access to all your messages, "
"contacts, files, and more, forever."
msgstr "Uw account uitschakelen houdt in dat u de toegang tot al uw berichten, contacten, bestanden en meer voor altijd zult verliezen."

#. Translators: Deactivation is a permanent action that occurs on the server.
#: src/account_settings/general_page/deactivate_account_subpage.blp:57
msgid ""
"To confirm that you really want to deactivate this account, type in your "
"Matrix user ID:"
msgstr "Voer uw Matrix-ID in om te bevestigen dat u deze account echt wilt uitschakelen:"

#: src/account_settings/general_page/log_out_subpage.rs:83
msgid ""
"The crypto identity and account recovery are not set up properly. If this is "
"your last connected session and you have no recent local backup of your "
"encryption keys, you will not be able to restore your account."
msgstr "De versleutelingsidentiteit en accountherstel zijn niet juist ingesteld. Als dit uw laatst verbonden sessie is en u heeft geen recente lokale back-up van uw versleutelingssleutels, zult u niet in staat zijn om uw account te herstellen."

#: src/account_settings/general_page/log_out_subpage.rs:91
msgid ""
"This is your last connected session. Make sure that you can still access "
"your recovery key or passphrase, or to backup your encryption keys before "
"logging out."
msgstr "Dit is uw laatst verbonden sessie. Zorg ervoor dat u nog steeds toegang hebt tot uw herstelsleutel of -wachtwoord, of om uw versleutelingssleutels te back-uppen, voordat u zich afmeldt."

